Subject: Re: [T2] idling problem

So the only change was a R&R & replace 2 heads? I would double-check
the timing, but my best guess would be you have a vacuum leak
somewhere that was caused during the R&R. I'd look for
something/anything that looks outta place or not hooked up well.

